      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This exceptional vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Maintained to an exacting standard, the exterior retains its original showroom luster, while the interior remains in flawless, as-new condition. A rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast seeking a vehicle of uncompromising quality and mechanical integrity.",
